OL,3,COil and gas windfall tax rise would
OL,4,Ccost the economy #13bn, trade body
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FIncreased windfall taxes on the UK's
OL,8,Foffshore oil and gas industries would
OL,9,Fcost the economy about #13 billion
OL,10,Fover the next five years and lead to a
OL,11,Ffall in tax receipts, a trade body has
OL,12,Fwarned.
OL,14,FAccording to figures published by
OL,15,FOffshore Energies UK (OEUK), the
OL,16,Fproposed increase in the Energy
OL,17,FProfits Levy (EPL) would see
OL,18,Finvestments in UK projects by oil and
OL,19,Fgas producers fall from an expected
OL,20,F#14.1 billion to just #2.3 billion
OL,21,Fbetween 2025 and 2029.
