OL,3,COil and gas windfall tax rise would
OL,4,Ccost the economy #13bn, trade body
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FThe report added that while expected
OL,8,Ftax take from the sector would
OL,9,Fincrease in the short term, a rapid
OL,10,Ffall in production triggered by the
OL,11,Floss of investment would result in a
OL,12,F#12 billion decrease in tax receipts.
OL,14,FUnder the Government's proposed
OL,15,Fchanges the EPL would rise to 38% from
OL,16,FNovember 1, which the OEUK says would
OL,17,Fpush the headline rate on upstream oil
OL,18,Fand gas activities up to 78%.
